Package uni

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • uni.Group
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IGroup
    public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGroup
    A group is set of students who, have something in common.

    The Group is a list of objects from Studentclass. There are operations, that can be applied to all of these objects.

    Author:
    Piotr Socha, Bartosz Sadowski, Mateusz Lysik
    See Also:
    Student
